    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Meratus Jasa Prima Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the construction, development, and operation of maritime infrastructure facilities and related services in Indonesia. The company manages and operates stevedoring in terminals; supplies and operates stevedoring equipment; operates and maintains equipment to support stevedoring, cargodoring, lift on/lift off, trucking, and receiving/delivery, as well as opening and closing of palka and shifting; and provides plugging service and reefer container monitoring in operation area terminal. It also offers truck, mechanic, and non mechanic facility; and implements lift on/lift off and delivery. In addition, the company is involved in trading, development, transportation, agrobusiness, and others; and provision of land transportation, repair shop, and other services. The company was formerly known as PT ICTSI Jasa Prima Tbk and changed its name to PT Meratus Jasa Prima Tbk in April 2024. The company was incorporated in 1978 and is headquartered in Jakarta Utara, Indonesia. PT Meratus Jasa Prima Tbk is a subsidiary of PT Saranakelola Investa.",
